      "creatureType": "",
      "blurb": "Male ash giant juju zombie",
      "publicNotes": "<h3>Conversion notes (this module)</h3><p><strong>Role:</strong> the donjon's porter (F8) — an <strong>ash giant</strong> kept servile by constant charms in life, hauling sacrifices down and bodies back up, until Prelate Aruth sacrificed <em>him</em> as part of his own mummy-rising rite. The curse stood the remains back up as a juju zombie that shambled to its old post and has waited five centuries for orders that will never come. <strong>Once he starts bellowing in a fight, @UUID[Compendium.cotct-pf2e-conversion.cotct-actors.Actor.prelateAruth0001]{Prelate Aruth} (F10, next door) comes to investigate.</strong> Pursues throughout the donjon but never exits it.</p>",
      "privateNotes": ""
