      "name": "Zombie Rot",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>An infected creature can't heal damage it takes from zombie rot until it has been cured of the disease.</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:33]</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> carrier with no ill effect (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r {2d6}[negative]]]{2d6 negative damage} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> [[/r {2d6}[negative]]]{2d6 negative damage} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> [[/r {2d6}[negative]]]{2d6 negative damage} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> dead, rising as a zombie immediately.</p>"
        },
